description:
Watch the full video here: https://youtu.be/v-FnIloVxUQ
How has our society become so self-centered, disrespectful, and entitled? Is there a better way?  Is it possible that we’ve forgotten our most foundational values? God has given us a clear path to freedom and happiness with Him and those around us. Join Unlocking Bible Prophecies as we explore the Ten Commandments and what they mean, how they apply and if they still have any significance in the life of a Christian. Watch this sneak peek and tune in to learn about The Way and head over to @Adventist World Radio,  awr.org/bible to watch the full video.
